# libosock - C++ socket library
----------

This project is an attempt to build simple to use, yet efficient object-oriented
C++ Library for sockets and SSL.

In order to build this library you might need to:

- get libraries that libosock is linked against:
sudo apt-get install libssl-dev		TODO: make a check for it in autotools
sudo apt-get install libboost-dev	TODO: make a check for it in autotools

- get tools required to build the library
sudo apt-get install automake
sudo apt-get install libtool
